      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i guess. but it feels more than just being lonely. it feels like i've already faded out. like there's zero impact. if i just... stopped showing up for work or stopped responding to texts, would it even change anything for anyone? it feels like the world would just keep spinning like i was never even part of it.",
